### Describe the bug

When using CDI decorators with generic type parameters in a Quarkus application, a `NoSuchMethodError` is thrown when invoking a decorated method. The error message indicates that it cannot find the method in the decorator class.

The following configuration fails when executing the `GreetingResource.hello()` method:

```java
interface Repository<T> {
  T get();
}

@Priority(APPLICATION)
@Decorator
class LoggingRepository<T> implements Repository<T> {

  @Inject Logger logger;

  @Inject @Any @Delegate Repository<T> delegate;

  @Override
  public T get() {
    logger.debug("Getting item");
    return delegate.get();
  }
}

@ApplicationScoped
class GreetingRepository implements Repository<String> {

  @Override
  public String get() {
    return "Hello from RESTEasy Reactive";
  }
}

@Path("/hello")
class GreetingResource {

  @Inject GreetingRepository repository;

  @GET
  @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_PLAIN)
  public String hello() {
    return repository.get();
  }
}
```

The exception is:

```
	Suppressed: java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: 'java.lang.String org.acme.LoggingRepository.get()'
		at org.acme.GreetingRepository_Subclass.get(Unknown Source)
		at org.acme.GreetingRepository_ClientProxy.get(Unknown Source)
		at org.acme.GreetingResource.hello(GreetingResource.java:53)
		at org.acme.GreetingResource$quarkusrestinvoker$hello_e747664148511e1e5212d3e0f4b40d45c56ab8a1.invoke(Unknown Source)
		at org.jboss.resteasy.reactive.server.handlers.InvocationHandler.handle(InvocationHandler.java:29)
		at io.quarkus.resteasy.reactive.server.runtime.QuarkusResteasyReactiveRequestContext.invokeHandler(QuarkusResteasyReactiveRequestContext.java:141)
		at org.jboss.resteasy.reactive.common.core.AbstractResteasyReactiveContext.run(AbstractResteasyReactiveContext.java:145)
```

A similar configuration works as expected in Weld.

### Expected behavior

Quarkus Arc decorates all beans that implement the interface with the decorator and no exception is thrown. In this example, the `GreetingRepository` is decorated with logic in the `LoggingRepository<T>` decorator.

### Actual behavior

Decorated bean throws `NoSuchMethodException`.

